Hey FRC teams!

Have you ever wanted to turn your CAD models into stunning, photorealistic renders? Whether you‚Äôre designing a robot reveal, working on sponsor presentations, or just want to create cool visuals for your team, SOLIDWORKS Visualize is the tool for you!

What is SOLIDWORKS Visualize?
It‚Äôs a powerful rendering tool that works with any CAD file‚Äîso even if you‚Äôre using SOLIDWORKS, Onshape, Fusion, or Inventor, you can still bring your models into Visualize and create high-quality images & animations.

Why Should FRC Teams Use It?
Showcase your robot in the best light before it‚Äôs even built
Impress sponsors with professional-looking presentations
Make reveal videos & animations that stand out
Easy-to-use‚ÄîNo advanced rendering experience needed!

If you‚Äôre using SOLIDWORKS for FRC, you already have access to Visualize Standard for free! If not, you can still try it out with the SOLIDWORKS Student Edition or ask your team‚Äôs mentors about getting it through FIRST sponsorship.
